The paper focuses on developing a programming framework for safe robotics systems, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the challenges of using third-party components and machine learning techniques, which are common topics in software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper proposes an integrated runtime assurance system, which is related to control systems (cs.SY) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.RO, cs.SE, and cs.SY, followed by cs.AI and cs.CR.
